snippet.title: Wobbledogs Console Edition - Announcement Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Wobbledogs Console Edition is coming to Nintendo Switch on November 17, 2022! Pre-order today: https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/wobbledogs-console-edition-switch/

Wobbledogs Console Edition is a casual and chill sandbox experience for players of all ages who want to care for their very own virtual pets in a surprising, unique and stress-free environment.

#Wobbledogs #IndieWorld #NintendoSwitch

Subscribe for more Nintendo fun! https://goo.gl/HYYsot

Visit Nintendo.com for all the latest! http://www.nintendo.com/
